    "plan_content": "Here's the full implementation plan I've designed after studying all the relevant code:\n\n---\n\n## What I'll Build\n\n### 4 file changes — 2 new, 2 registry appends\n\n### `ui/stepper.tsx` — Architecture\n\n**Two stacked React contexts** (same pattern as `carousel.tsx`):\n- `StepperContext` → provided by `<Stepper>`, shares `activeStep` + `orientation`\n- `StepperItemContext` → provided by `<StepperItem>`, shares `step` + computed `state`\n\n**7 named exports:**\n\n| Component | Element | Key behaviour |\n|-----------|---------|---------------|\n| `Stepper` | `<div data-slot=\"stepper\">` | Provider root; `flex-row` or `flex-col` based on orientation |\n| `StepperItem` | `<div data-slot=\"stepper-item\" data-step data-state>` | Computes `state` (`completed`/`active`/`pending`) from `activeStep` in context |\n| `StepperTrigger` | `<button data-slot=\"stepper-trigger\">` | Uses **cva** for 3 state-based visual styles; shows step number as default child |\n| `StepperTitle` | `<p data-slot=\"stepper-title\">` | `text-sm font-medium` |\n| `StepperDescription` | `<p data-slot=\"stepper-description\">` | `text-xs text-muted-foreground` |\n| `StepperSeparator` | `<div data-slot=\"stepper-separator\">` | Reads **both** contexts; `h-px flex-1` (horizontal) or `w-px` (vertical); `bg-primary` when completed |\n| `StepperContent` | `<div data-slot=\"stepper-content\">` | Returns `null` when `step !== activeStep` |\n\n**cva variants** for `StepperTrigger`:\n- `completed` → `bg-primary text-primary-foreground` (filled circle)\n- `active` → `border-2 border-primary bg-background text-primary` (outlined, primary colour)\n- `pending` → `border-2 border-border bg-background text-muted-foreground` (outlined, muted)\n\n### `examples/stepper-demo.tsx`\n- `\"use client\"` + `React.useState(1)` for activeStep\n- 3 steps: Account / Profile / Complete, each with Trigger + Title + Description + Separator (last step omits separator)\n- 3 `StepperContent` panels (only active one renders)\n- Previous / Next `<Button>` controls\n\n### Registry entries\n- **`ui/_registry.ts`**: `name: \"stepper\"`, `dependencies: [\"class-variance-authority\"]` (cva explicit since no Radix UI — same precedent as `spinner`)\n- **`examples/_registry.ts`**: `name: \"stepper-demo\"`, `registryDependencies: [\"stepper\"]`",
